#
# ADR-0009: PKCE for OIDC login sources. Stock Gitea, acting as an OIDC client,
# never sends a PKCE code_challenge, so identity providers that require PKCE
# reject the sign-in (not fixable via config/overlay/plugin). The patch adds the
# S256 challenge, gated to the openidConnect provider.
# Upstream (deletion path — drop these once merged): go-gitea/gitea#34747,
# go-gitea/gitea#21376. Ported onto v1.26.2 (module rename only; PKCE unit tests
# pass on the stable line).
